column5: Yes folks They will race in the rain. Only in Canada.LOL  Should be very interesting.
Fellows, Carpentier and Villenueve are doing well at this point. Be great to see a Canadian 1,2,3 finish.
Right now those cars could use a 250 merc straped to thier behinds.LOL Hydro nascar.LOL
Fellows, Carpentier and Villenueve are doing well at this point. Be great to see a Canadian 1,2,3 finish
We got 1,2 and it was great to see the cup guys, saying it was fun.LOL
Villeneuve came close. Tough luck wiping out that close to the call.  JF
I couldn't believe that there were more accidents during cautions than green flag racing! Congratulations to Ron Fellows from Mississauga
